Package: beatbox
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libgtk2.0-0 (>= 2.18.0), libgee2 (>= 0.5.0), gstreamer0.10-plugins-base, libtag1c2a, libwebkit-1.0-2, libxml2, libgconf2-4 (>= 2.22.0), libnotify1, libunique-1.0-0 (>= 1.0.0), libsoup2.4-1 (>= 2.26.0), libdbus-glib-1-2 (>= 0.80), libsqlheavy-bin
Description: An easy to use music player and library manager.
 BeatBox music player is an easy to use, stable, fast, and good
 looking music library organizer. It has many modern features
 including Last.FM integration to download artwork, information, and scrobble your music, 
 Playlists and Smart Playlists,find music similar to the currently playing song, 
 simple User Interface, fast searching for music, queue system, mass song editing and more.
